    <item>
      <title>马杜罗寻求对其新国家养老基金向企业征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/maduro-seeks-to-tax-businesses-for-his-new-state-pension-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府提议对私营企业征收高达其工资 15% 的税，以建立国家养老基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/maduro-seeks-to-tax-businesses-for-his-new-state-pension-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰在腐败整顿后收紧军事采购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/ukraine-tightens-military-procurement-after-corruption-shakeup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名高级安全官员表示，在腐败指控导致乌克兰国防部领导层改组八个月后，乌克兰国防部对其采购系统进行了全面改革，并加强了与北约的合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/ukraine-tightens-military-procurement-after-corruption-shakeup</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查：外国干预并未影响加拿大选举结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/foreign-meddling-didn-t-impact-canada-election-outcome-inquiry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项公开调查得出的结论是，中国在过去两次加拿大选举中进行了一些干预，但没有影响总体结果或破坏选举的完整性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/foreign-meddling-didn-t-impact-canada-election-outcome-inquiry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:05:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西希望淡水河谷下一任首席执行官与政府更加接近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/brazil-wants-vale-s-next-ceo-to-have-closer-ties-with-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西预计，全球第二大铁矿石生产商淡水河谷公司的下一任首席执行官将与官员和监管机构建立更密切的关系，尽管公众对政府对公司继任计划的影响力的审查扰乱了今年早些时候的领导层搜寻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/brazil-wants-vale-s-next-ceo-to-have-closer-ties-with-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
